name: executesUserLifecycleWithJourneyAndRipper(Quest)
description: Executes the user lifecycle with @Journey data setup and @Ripper cleanup after the test.
descriptionHtml:
Test Details
PropertyValue
Test NameexecutesUserLifecycleWithJourneyAndRipper
Class NameBasicToAdvancedEvolutionTest
Class Annotations
@SpringBootTest(,
     args=,
     classes=class io.cyborgcode.roa.framework.config.TestConfig,
     properties=,
     webEnvironment=NONE)
@Tag(exclude-from-verify)
@API
Method Annotations
@Test
@Regression
@AuthenticateViaApi(type=class io.cyborgcode.api.test.framework.api.authentication.AppAuth,
     credentials=class io.cyborgcode.api.test.framework.api.authentication.AdminAuth)
@PreQuest(
@io.cyborgcode.roa.framework.annotation.Journey(journeyData={
    @io.cyborgcode.roa.framework.annotation.JourneyData( "USER_INTERMEDIATE")
    }  "CREATE_NEW_USER")
@io.cyborgcode.roa.framework.annotation.Journey(journeyData={
    @io.cyborgcode.roa.framework.annotation.JourneyData( "USER_LEADER")
    }  "CREATE_NEW_USER"))
@Ripper(targets=DELETE_ADMIN_USER)
@Description(Executes the user lifecycle with
@Journey data setup and
@Ripper cleanup after the test.)
Test ArgumentsQuest
